<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>About - Celestial Gatherings</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron&family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Platypi:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&display=swap">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        .about-hero {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 56vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 16px;
            background:
                    linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(13,27,42,0.85), rgba(13,27,42,0.8)),
                    url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1446776811953-b23d57bd21aa?q=80&w=1600&auto=format&fit=crop') center/cover no-repeat;
            color: var(--txt-light);
        }
        .about-hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Platypi', serif;
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            margin-bottom: .5rem;
        }
        .about-hero p {
            max-width: 820px;
            margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
            opacity: .95;
        }
        .about-hero .btn {
            margin: .25rem .35rem;
            border-radius: .65rem;
            padding: .7rem 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--bg-primary);
            border-color: var(--bg-primary);
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { background-color: var(--bg-primary-hover); border-color: var(--bg-primary-hover); }
        .btn-outline-light { border-width: 2px; }

        .section {
            padding: 56px 0;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Platypi', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--txt-light);
        }
        .section-subtle { color: #cfd6dc; }

        /* cards */
        .feature-card, .stat-card, .timeline-item, .quote-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 18px 18px;
            color: var(--txt-light);
        }
        .feature-card i {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-right: .5rem;
            color: var(--link);
        }
        .feature-card h5 { margin: .5rem 0 .25rem; }

        /* stats */
        .stat-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 22px 16px;
        }
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .stat-label { color: #cfd6dc; margin-top: .35rem; }

        /* timeline */
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 22px;
        }
        .timeline:before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 8px;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 2px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }
        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .timeline-item:before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: -14px;
            top: 12px;
            width: 10px; height: 10px;
            background: var(--link);
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(160,193,209,0.25);
        }
        .timeline-item h6 { margin: 0 0 .25rem; }

        .quote-card blockquote {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: #e8ecf1;
        }
        .quote-card .cite {
            margin-top: .5rem;
            color: #cfd6dc;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: .95rem;
        }

        /* CTA */
        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 36px 20px;
            background:
                    radial-gradient(1200px 400px at 50% -10%, rgba(160,193,209,.15), rgba(0,0,0,0) 70%),
                    linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(65,90,119,.12), rgba(13,27,42,0));
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border-radius: 14px;
        }
        .cta h3 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: .35rem; }
        .cta p { color: #cfd6dc; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="about-hero">
    <div>
        <h1>About Celestial Gatherings</h1>
        <p>We bring together stargazers, space geeks, and the astro-curious to learn, share, and explore the night sky—through meetups, talks, and unforgettable viewing events.</p>
        <div>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/events"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt mr-1"></i> Browse Events</a>
            <% if (!user) { %>
                <a class="btn btn-outline-light" href="/user/signup"><i class="fas fa-user-plus mr-1"></i> Join the Community</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a class="btn btn-outline-light" href="/events/new"><i class="fas fa-plus mr-1"></i> Host an Event</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT WE DO -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">What We Do</h2>
        <p class="section-subtle mb-4">Community-driven events that make space science welcoming and fun.</p>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="feature-card h-100">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-meteor"></i><h5 class="mb-0">Star Parties</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mb-0 mt-2">Guided night-sky viewing with telescopes, constellations, and astrophotography tips.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="feature-card h-100">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i><h5 class="mb-0">Talks & Workshops</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mb-0 mt-2">From beginner astronomy to deep-space missions—hands-on and friendly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="feature-card h-100">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i><h5 class="mb-0">Community</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mb-0 mt-2">Connect with local clubs and new friends who love looking up as much as you do.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">In Numbers</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-6 col-md-3 mb-3">
                <div class="stat-card h-100">
                    <div class="stat-number">3.1k</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Members</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6 col-md-3 mb-3">
                <div class="stat-card h-100">
                    <div class="stat-number">480+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Events Hosted</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6 col-md-3 mb-3">
                <div class="stat-card h-100">
                    <div class="stat-number">22</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Cities</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6 col-md-3 mb-3">
                <div class="stat-card h-100">
                    <div class="stat-number">94%</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">5★ Feedback</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-7 mb-3">
                <div class="timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <h6><i class="fas fa-user-plus mr-1 text-info"></i> Create your account</h6>
                        <p class="mb-0">Join free and set your interests (beginner, astrophotography, rocket launches, etc.).</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <h6><i class="fas fa-calendar-check mr-1 text-info"></i> RSVP or host</h6>
                        <p class="mb-0">Grab a spot at upcoming events—or host your own and invite the community.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <h6><i class="fas fa-star mr-1 text-info"></i> Show up & look up</h6>
                        <p class="mb-0">We’ll bring the schedule and tips. You bring curiosity (and maybe a blanket).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-5 mb-3">
                <div class="quote-card h-100">
                    <blockquote>“I found my first dark-sky party through Celestial Gatherings and ended up meeting my local astro club. Now I’m out there every new moon.”</blockquote>
                    <div class="cite">— Maya R., member since 2024</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CALL TO ACTION -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="cta">
            <h3>Ready to explore the night sky with us?</h3>
            <p>Browse upcoming events—or start one in your city.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary mr-2" href="/events"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt mr-1"></i> See Events</a>
            <% if (!user) { %>
                <a class="btn btn-outline-light" href="/user/signup"><i class="fas fa-user-plus mr-1"></i> Sign Up</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a class="btn btn-outline-light" href="/events/new"><i class="fas fa-plus mr-1"></i> Create Event</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>

